# Plan: Consistent project filtering across trace commands (#737)

## Problem

When a user provides `org/project/trace-id`, only `span list` actually filters by project. Other commands silently discard the project segment — inconsistent UX.

## Approach: API-level filtering everywhere

Every command filters server-side. No client-side tree walking.

| Command | Mechanism | Notes |
|---------|-----------|-------|
| `span list` | ✅ Already works — `project:{slug}` in query | No changes to filtering |
| `trace view` | Pass numeric project ID to API instead of `-1` | Need `getProject()` call for slug→ID |
| `trace logs` | `project:{slug}` in query param | Same pattern as span list |
| `log list` (trace mode) | `project:{slug}` in query param | Same pattern as span list |

For `trace view` orphaned spans (parent is in another project): note it, no supplemental fetch. If the user wants the full tree, the hint gives them the exact command.

Multi-project: `--query 'project:[cli,backend]'` works on any command with `--query` via Sentry's in-list search syntax. Document in flag briefs and docs.

## Hints: always copy-pasteable with real values

Hints must interpolate actual org, project, and trace ID so the user can copy-paste directly. Examples of what they'll look like at runtime:

**When filtered** (`trace view my-org/cli-server/abc123...`):
```
Filtered to project 'cli-server'. Full trace: sentry trace view my-org/abc123def456abc123def456abc12345
```

**When unfiltered and multi-project** (`trace view abc123...`):
```
This trace spans 4 projects (cli, cli-server, sentry, release-registry). Filter: sentry trace view my-org/cli-server/abc123def456abc123def456abc12345
```

**Trace logs filtered** (`trace logs my-org/cli-server/abc123...`):
```
Filtered to project 'cli-server'. Full trace logs: sentry trace logs my-org/abc123def456abc123def456abc12345
Multi-project filter: sentry trace logs abc123def456abc123def456abc12345 -q 'project:[cli-server,api]'
```

**Span list multi-project query hint** (on `span list <trace-id>` with no project):
```
Filter by project: sentry span list my-org/cli-server/abc123def456abc123def456abc12345
```

